Technology has developed increasingly in recent years .
As a result of this , our society has changed a lot .
On the one hand , technology has made our lives more comfortable and easier .
On the other hand , we have faced some problems , such as social and environmental problems .
Nowadays the students have much more facilitis in our education than before .
Although in those days the only way of learning was reading .
These days we can use the computer , television and some sophisticated equipment , which were unusuall before .
Than of the technology , we can reach any place in the world easily .
We can get some information more quickly .
technology has a huge effect on our spare time activity as well .
Children play on the computer instead of usuall plays .
Despite a huge facilitie of technology has affected our lives negatively .
There has been a change in relatinships of between people .
People are getting more and more lonely .
We have noticed the necessary damage in recent years .
While we are using technology , we should take into consideration the environment .
We should not allow technology to be exploited in the world .
If we want to leave a good world for the next generations , we should behave more respectfully againgst . . the nature .
