Technical and Warm home and people 's way of life has considerably been changed by rapdily developing mordern technology .
To begin with , it will be good to look back on how our parents have lived in the house .
50 years ago , Korean mothers should have made a fire by burning woods to warm the room up and make food .
Since the eletric fire and microwave ovens have been invented , their life has been far easier than before .
Today , however , people do not need to spend many times on making food , washing up , or even on turning on the off the light .
Machines , such as a dish washer , laundry machine and remote controllers help us jut to relax or do a little work but is necessary .
From my point of view , people 's home in the future will be controlled by a computer which is devised in every machine , TV , cooker and the light , connecting to the owner .
He / she can just press the button or send your e - mail to know what he / she needs , even though the owner is far from the house .
On the other hand , people will still be living in a building which is constructed for a " family " .
In spite of the computer , the children will need food their mothers make and love expressed not by a computer , but by parents themselves .
Computer might know better than human , but there are many things which it can not replace in our life .
