How has has modern technology changed our daily life ?
Modern technology has changed a lot of our daily life .
On one hand , nowadays if we have to travel to Paris and to return in the same day you can take a plane without any problem .
In the past , it was impossible to go to Paris from Barcelona and come back in one day .
Another advantage is that if you go on an excursion and you take your mobile phone , if you get lost somebody could find you .
I think that the most important modern technology in these days is the internet .
With technology , you can do whatever you want without going out to home , ( shopping , speaking with a friend , working , putting your money aside .... )
On the other hand , the main disadvantage is that using modern machines , it can be very difficult for the people ; it would be very pratitable if the modern industrie train people about using modern technologies .
To sum up , modern technology has change my a lot of our daily life and this is going to increase .
