Subject : About the daily life at our school .
Introduction
This report is the aim to research the students about their daily life at school and give some suggestion about it .
What do students do now ?
Lots of students normally have classes in the morning .
And sometimes they do something in the library by themselves in the school .
For instance , reading , looking for some information or using computer .
What do they think about it ?
The art and students want to learn another foreign language .
Moreover , some foreign students hope there will be some English classes that aim for the examination .
Most of them want to do more activities in the afternoon .
Recommendations
Open some foreign language classes at part - time for the students who are interested in it .
Let foreign students do more excises from Englishs to help them pass the exam .
Using the equipment and areas that we have to organise some activities .
